Food Travel: 🇺🇸 + 🇰🇷 + 🇸🇬
.
MUSH HAVE ROOM FOR SHROOMS Pt. 1 - homemade trio mushroom cream soup 🍄🥣 drizzled with thick cream and white truffle oil + baked portobello mushroom with cheddar and mozzarella cheese 🧀 and cherry tomatoes (reminiscent of the ones made by my cousin for Christmas many years ago 😊) + Korean-inspired cheesy garlic butter 🧄 🧈 toast + pan-seared apple baked ham + goreng pisang 🍌 from nbr’s daughter (so sweet of her, esp when I felt like having bananas)
